"title": "8751: false witness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8751: false witness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The telling of lies about another so as to make them appear guilty when they are innocent. Condemned in Scripture, false witness was experienced by Jesus Christ and is to be expected by those who follow him.</p>\n<h2>False witness is condemned in Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1\">EXO 23:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:15-Deut19:19\">DEU 19:15–19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:5-Ps101:7\">PSA 101:5–101:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:18\">MAT 19:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a></p>\n<h2>False witness arises from an evil heart</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:19–15:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h2>False witness will be subject to judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:5-Ps101:8\">PSA 101:5–101:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:28\">PRO 21:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:9\">PRO 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:24\">DAN 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:35-Matt12:37\">MAT 12:35–12:37</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who were the victims of false witness</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:59-Matt26:61\">MAT 26:59–26:61</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:55-Mark14:59\">MRK 14:55–14:59</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:18-Matt11:19\">MAT 11:18–11:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:33-Luke7:34\">LUK 7:33–7:34</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:8-1Kgs21:14\">1KI 21:8–21:14</a> <em>Naboth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:12\">PSA 27:12</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:24\">DAN 6:24</a> <em>Daniel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:11-Acts6:13\">ACT 6:11–6:13</a> <em>Stephen</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:5-Acts17:7\">ACT 17:5–17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:5-Acts24:9\">ACT 24:5–24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:7\">ACT 25:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:8\">ROM 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>False witness against believers is to be expected by them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:22–6:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9-Matt24:10\">MAT 24:9–24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:9\">ACT 19:9</a></p>",
